    <string name="battery_optimization_message">"If Panda is not working properly, this might be due to intense battery optimization by your device manufacturer.

Manufacturers like Samsung, Huawei, OnePlus, Xiaomi, and others often add aggressive battery optimizations that can break Panda's functionality.

To fix this, you need to disable battery optimizations specifically for Panda in your device settings."</string>
